</fig><p class="- topic/p ">To access, expand <menucascade class="+ topic/ph ui-d/menucascade "><uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Config</uicontrol>
<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Services</uicontrol><uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">OrionAlarmService</uicontrol>
<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">RdbAlarmDatabaseConversion</uicontrol></menucascade> and
double-click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">SourceName</uicontrol>.</p></section>
